condition.narrative: An internal auditor for the OMVG Secretariat to be recruited no later than 3 months after the Effective Date, with qualificationsand experience satisfactory to the Association.
The Participating Countries and OMVG shall establish the Monitoring and Advisory Committee.
The Recipient shall all measures required on its part to ensure that the Asset Management Agency be established no later than 24months after the Effective Date.

The Recipient shall establish a National Monitoring Committee with composition, functions and resources satisfactory to theAssociation and, within applicable local government units, Local Monitoring and Advisory Committees with composition andresponsibilities in form and substance satisfactory to the Association, as further described in the ESMP and the ProjectImplementation Manual.

The Recipient shall take all measures required on its part to ensure that each of the Kaleta Power Purchase Agreements and theTransmission Service Agreements shall have become effective by the date which is 12 months after the Effective Date.
The owners engineer has been recruited no later than 4 months after the Effective Date
